    Page: 471
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Thoughts
---
The power of thought is a mental dynamic of enormously powerful energy. It
has been responsible for the soaring of humankind to the heights of
achievement, and likewise for the sinking of man to the depths of
degradation.
